WEBVTT

00:00.150 --> 00:01.956
Previously on "Shots Fired"...

00:01.979 --> 00:04.061
It's possible that all I've accomplished

00:04.129 --> 00:06.455
will be overshadowed by the
deaths of these two young men.

00:08.377 --> 00:10.585
Beck was having a bad day,
it doesn't make him a murderer.

00:10.650 --> 00:12.352
- It makes him a liar.
- I heard this was your last week.

00:12.375 --> 00:13.828
- Going out with a bang?
- Might as well.

00:13.851 --> 00:16.027
I'll follow when you are
capable of leading.

00:16.091 --> 00:17.262
Kerry!

00:18.986 --> 00:21.259
I just spoke to Kiana. Where...?

00:21.821 --> 00:23.261
There's a young woman in surgery

00:23.327 --> 00:25.128
- fighting for her life.
- It's nothing to do with me.

00:25.151 --> 00:27.120
Why am I not surprised to see
you here, Brother Terry?

00:27.143 --> 00:28.905
She's being charged with
the murder of Joey Campbell.

00:28.929 --> 00:30.592
You recorded us?

00:30.657 --> 00:33.441
- Drop this custody suit.
- You're unfit to be a mother.

00:33.506 --> 00:35.425
Assaulting an officer, resisting arrest?

00:35.491 --> 00:36.872
It won't get you your daughter back.

